  <h2 align="center" property="term:title">Observed Distribution of Meningitis in Historical Record</h2>
  <p align="left" property="term:description">This map shows the distribution of observed meningitis epidemics during 1841-1999.</p>
<p align="left">
These data are based on the accounts of epidemics attributed to meningococci documented in published literature and internal institutional reports.</p>

<p> The World Health Organization (WHO) proposes the use of epidemic thresholds for the early detection of epidemics and improved control responses. This map is a useful tool in defining 'at-risk' areas in critical need of increased monitoring activities and epidemic preparedness.</p>


